---
const items = [
	{
		question: 'Can I get a free estimate?',
		answer: `Yes you can! We will always provide you the exact price of our services on-site before any work has been done. If agreed on, work can start that same day.`,
	},
	{
		question: 'How do your services work?',
		answer: ``,
	},
	{
		question: 'How much does it cost?',
		answer: `Depending on the pest-type, size, and severity of your situation, costs can vary. After your free pest inspection, we will provide you with the entire price of treatment on location. The rest is up to you!`,
	},
	{
		question: 'Will you be able to remove pests permanently?',
		answer: `Yes we can and yes we will! Our pest control service providers are here for one thing: to get rid of pests! We also provide our customers seasonal services and preventative measures to keep your home pest-free during those nastier seasons!`,
	},
	{
		question: "What if I'm not happy with the results?",
		answer: `Nobody is perfect, including us. On the rare occasion where you are not happy with our pest control services, let us know. We will give you your money back (but not those pests). Simple as that, no questions asked.`,
	},
];
---

<section class="bg-custom-light-blue">
	<div class="px-4 py-16 mx-auto max-w-7xl">
		<div class="max-w-xl sm:mx-auto lg:max-w-2xl py-4 pt-8 sm:py-6 lg:py-8 lg:pt-12">
			<div class="max-w-xl mb-10 md:mx-auto text-center lg:max-w-2xl md:mb-12">
				<h2
					class="max-w-lg mb-4 text-3xl leading-none tracking-tight sm:text-4xl md:mx-auto font-heading text-custom-blue-two"
				>
					Frequently Asked Questions
				</h2>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div
			id="accordion-color"
			data-accordion="closed"
			data-active-classes="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 text-black dark:text-white"
			data-inactive-classes="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 text-black dark:text-white"
			class="bg-white rounded-t-xl"
		>
			<h2 id="accordion-color-heading-1">
				<button
					type="button"
					class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-5 font-bold text-left border border-b-0 border-gray-200 rounded-t-xl bg-white text-black"
					data-accordion-target="#accordion-color-body-1"
					aria-expanded="true"
					aria-controls="accordion-color-body-1"
				>
					<span>{items[0].question}</span>
					<svg
						data-accordion-icon=""
						class="w-6 h-6 rotate-180 shrink-0"
						fill="currentColor"
						viewBox="0 0 20 20"
						xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
						><path
							fill-rule="evenodd"
							d="M5.293 7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 010-1.414z"
							clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
					</svg>
				</button>
			</h2>
			<div id="accordion-color-body-1" class="bg-white" aria-labelledby="accordion-color-heading-1">
				<div class="p-5 font-light border border-b-0 border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 bg-white">
					<p class="mb-2 text-black dark:text-gray-400">
						{items[0].answer}
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<h2 id="accordion-color-heading-2">
				<button
					type="button"
					class="flex items-center bg-white text-black justify-between w-full p-5 font-bold text-left border border-b-0 border-gray-200"
					data-accordion-target="#accordion-color-body-2"
					aria-expanded="false"
					aria-controls="accordion-color-body-2"
				>
					<span>{items[1].question}</span>
					<svg
						data-accordion-icon=""
						class="w-6 h-6 shrink-0"
						fill="currentColor"
						viewBox="0 0 20 20"
						xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
						><path
							fill-rule="evenodd"
							d="M5.293 7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 010-1.414z"
							clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
					</svg>
				</button>
			</h2>
			<div id="accordion-color-body-2" class="hidden" aria-labelledby="accordion-color-heading-2">
				<div class="p-5 font-light border border-b-0 border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
					<ol class="pl-5 text-black list-disc dark:text-gray-400">
						<li>Give us a call - speak with a qualified representative to help us understand the problem</li>
						<li>Schedule an inspection - earlier the better, we don't want pests multiplying!</li>
						<li>
							Exterminator Services - our pest technician(s) will arrive and assess what services are needed during the
							inspection. We will provide you the exact cost and treatment needed on location. If you agree, we can
							start work that same day!
						</li>
					</ol>
				</div>
			</div>
			<h2 id="accordion-color-heading-3">
				<button
					type="button"
					class="flex items-center bg-white text-black justify-between w-full p-5 font-bold text-left border border-b-0 border-gray-200"
					data-accordion-target="#accordion-color-body-3"
					aria-expanded="false"
					aria-controls="accordion-color-body-3"
				>
					<span>{items[2].question}</span>
