					<span>{items[4].question}</span>
					<svg
						data-accordion-icon=""
						class="w-6 h-6 shrink-0"
						fill="currentColor"
						viewBox="0 0 20 20"
						xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
						><path
							fill-rule="evenodd"
							d="M5.293 7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0L10 10.586l3.293-3.293a1 1 0 111.414 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 010-1.414z"
							clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
					</svg>
				</button>
			</h2>
			<div id="accordion-color-body-5" class="hidden" aria-labelledby="accordion-color-heading-5">
				<div class="p-5 font-light border border-t-0 border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
					<p class="mb-2 text-black dark:text-gray-400">
						Nobody is perfect, including us. On the rare occasion where you are not happy with our pest control
						services, let us know. We will give you your money back (but not those pests). Simple as that, no questions
						asked.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="max-w-screen-xl sm:mx-auto"></div>
	</div>
</section>
